T1  - Nonparametric estimation of structural models for high-frequency currency market data
AU  - Bansal, Ravi
AU  - Gallant, A.Ronald
AU  - Hussey, Robert
AU  - Tauchen, George
JO  - Journal of Econometrics
VL  - 66
IS  - 1
SP  - 251
