T1  - A numerical bayesian test for cointegration of AR processes
AU  - Dorfman, Jeffrey H.
JO  - Journal of Econometrics
VL  - 66
IS  - 1
SP  - 289
EP  - 324
PY  - 1995
DA  - 1995/03/01/
SN  - 0304-4076
